channel.title: Stuck at unpacking interfaces
channel.description:
I was replacing all my prayer icons with images that are all 28x28, and now my client gets stuck at unpacking interfaces, even though I have repacked the cache.
I'm not sure if there is a way to fix this or if there are too many colors.
I am using the new RuneScape icons like so: http://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/Thick_Skin
My client is the original Project Insanity client.
